&lt;p&gt;This is a wonderful opportunity to obtain a second to none training experience in a wide range of paediatric clinical specialities. The 9 month rotations include a range of acute, hospital based teams, our early years service at the Child Developmental Centre as well as the Special and Mainstream Schools teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be supported to develop your paediatric skill set by your peers and senior staff who are experts in their field and part of a large integrated physiotherapy and occupational therapy service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are ready to take your professional skills to the next level, have the right attributes to get the best out of children and young people and are ready for a new challenge we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
